## 📚 Documentation & Conventions

**All architectural and coding patterns are documented in the `.ai/` directory.**

### Quick Reference

**Start Here:**
- `.ai/AI_PROTOCOL.md` - How to work with this repo

**Platform Core:**
- `.ai/bioloop/architecture.md` - System architecture
- `.ai/bioloop/api_conventions.md` - API patterns
- `.ai/bioloop/ui_conventions.md` - UI patterns
- `.ai/bioloop/worker_conventions.md` - Worker patterns
- `.ai/bioloop/database_patterns.m Database patterns
- `.ai/bioloop/pitfalls.md` - Common mistakes
- `.ai/bioloop/features/*.md` - Platform features

### Priority Order of Truth

1. `.ai/bioloop/features/<feature>.md` (highest - feature-specific)
2. `.ai/bioloop/*.md` (platform conventions)
3. Repository code
4. Chat history (lowest)

**Chats explore. Changelogs decide. Files persist.**

